{"article_id":"Sj1Hdgoz1deVJzDd","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Divers have rescued four more boys from a vast cave system in northern Thailand on the second day of a complex operation .","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"The Thai Navy Seals","depth":12},{"id":2,"text":"leading the rescue operation","depth":12},{"id":3,"text":"have confirmed","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"that eight boys in total have been extracted .","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"Four boys and their football coach remain inside the caves .","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"Rescuers will try to free them on Tuesday .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"The group became trapped on 23 June","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"after heavy rains caused flooding ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"and was found last week by divers .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Four boys were brought out safely on Sunday ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"but the mission was paused overnight","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"for air tanks to be replaced .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"On Monday , air ambulances were seen departing from the area around the cave system","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"and ambulances were seen arriving at the hospital in the nearby town of Chiang Rai .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"The boys have not been seen in public ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"but have been pronounced to be in reasonable health .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"The rescue operation is complicated by sections in the cave","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"involving diving","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"- sometimes in very confined spaces -","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and climbing .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"The BBC 's Dan Johnson , at the scene , says","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"it is a careful , delicate operation fraught with risk .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"But he adds","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"that this daring , dangerous and complicated exercise is delivering success against difficult odds ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"and relief is starting to break the tension of the situation .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"After Monday 's operation had wound down for the day ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"rescue mission chief Narongsak Osottanakorn told reporters :","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"`` All four boys have arrived at hospital ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"all are safe . ''","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"the second day of the operation had gone more smoothly than the first ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"taking two hours less","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"as the procedure became more refined .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"Tuesday morning will see the start of attempts","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"to rescue the remaining four boys and the football coach .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"A massive pumping operation is said to have helped lower the water level inside the cave system ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"making the journey in and out easier","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"than it was .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"The Thai authorities say","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"the rescued boys are able to eat rice porridge ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"although their request for a favourite pork dish has been turned down","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"until their digestive systems recover from 10 days","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"without food .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"The government is strictly controlling information about the rescue .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"The names of the boys","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"who got out","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"have not been released ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"and even their parents have not been allowed to see them","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"- for health reasons ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"say Thai officials .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"Outside the hospital","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"where the boys were being received ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"there was a heavy police and media presence .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"Early in the afternoon , the sound of a helicopter thudded overhead .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"It was a sign","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that the rescue operation was going to plan .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"A few minutes later , a convoy with an ambulance swept through the streets","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"and swung into the hospital entrance .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"It was carrying the first boy","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"rescued on Monday .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Then","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"as dusk was falling ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"a small crowd of locals gathered outside the hospital .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Word was filtering out","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"that more boys had been rescued .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"People were straining to catch a glimpse of the unfolding drama .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"It came in the form of the flashing lights of three more ambulances -","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"signifying the rescue of three more boys .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"The rescue operation will resume on Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"It is not yet over","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"and is still fraught with danger .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"But people here are daring to believe what seemed impossible a little over a week ago -","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that all the boys and their coach will come out of the cave alive .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"A team of 90 expert divers","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"- 40 from Thailand and 50 from overseas -","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"has been working in the cave system .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"They have been guiding the boys through darkness and submerged passageways towards the mouth of the Tham Luang cave system .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Getting to and from where the boys are","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"has been an exhausting round trip , even for the experienced divers .","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"The process includes a mixture of walking , wading , climbing and diving along guide ropes","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"already in place .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"Wearing full-face masks ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"which are easier for novice divers than traditional respirators ,","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"each boy is being accompanied by two divers ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"who also carry his air supply .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"The toughest part is about halfway out at a section","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"named `` T-Junction '' ,","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"which is so tight","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"the divers have to take off their air tanks","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"to get through .","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"Beyond that a cavern","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"- called Chamber 3 -","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"has been turned into a forward base for the divers .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"There the boys can rest","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"before making the last , easier walk out to the entrance .","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"They are then taken to hospital in Chiang Rai .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"In an indication","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"of how dangerous the journey can be ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"a former Thai navy diver died in the caves on Friday .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"Saman Gunan was returning from a mission","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"to provide the group with air tanks","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"when he ran out of oxygen .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"He lost consciousness","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"and could not be revived .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"His colleagues said","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"they would `` not let the sacrifice of our friend go to waste '' .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"Some details have emerged of members of the team and their coach .","depth":4},{"id":108,"text":"Captain Duganpet Promtep , 13 , is described as a motivator and highly respected by his teammates .","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"He had apparently been scouted by several Thai professional clubs .","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"Myanmar-born Adul Sam-on , 14 , speaks several languages ,","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"and was the only team member","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"to be able to communicate with British divers","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"when they were first discovered .","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"It was 17-year-old Peerapat Sompiangjai 's birthday","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"when the group became trapped in the cave .","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"The snacks","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"the boys brought with them","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"to celebrate","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"are likely to have helped them survive their ordeal .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"Assistant coach Ekapol Chantawong , 25 , was said to be the weakest of the group","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"when they were found ,","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"as he reportedly refused to eat any of the food","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"and gave it instead to the boys .","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"The boys were found inside the cave by British rescue divers a week ago , about 4km","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"( 2.5 miles )","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"from the cave mouth .","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"Aged between 11 and 17 ,","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"they belong to a football club","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"called the Wild Boars ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"and became trapped during an excursion with their coach .","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"It took nine days to find them in the underground network 's dark depths .","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"The world football body Fifa has promised the boys seats at the World Cup final in Moscow on Sunday ,","depth":2},{"id":133,"text":"but it remains to be seen if they will be well enough","depth":3},{"id":134,"text":"to take up the offer .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":269,"left":266,"right":268,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"